{"word":"G3696 - ὅπλον - hóplon - hop'-lon - Armour","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὅπλον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>hóplon"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>hop'-lon"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Armour"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"ஆயுதம் - பால் வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. arms used in warfare, weapons"},{"paragraph":"2. an instrument"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Probably from the primary word <b>&#x03B5;&#x0314;&#x0301;&#x03C0;&#x03C9;</b> <b>hepo&#x0304;</b>(to be <i>busy</i> about); an <i>implement</i> or <i>utensil</i> or <i>tool</i> (literally or figuratively, especially offensive for war): - armour, instrument, weapon."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2528 - καθοπλίζω - kathoplízō - kath-op-lid'-zo/2528\">G2528</a>, <a href=\"#/G3695 - ὁπλίζω - hoplízō - hop-lid'-zo/3695\">G3695</a>, <a href=\"#/G3696 - ὅπλον - hóplon - hop'-lon/3696\">G3696</a>, <a href=\"#/G3833 - πανοπλία - panoplía - pan-op-lee'-ah/3833\">G3833</a>"}]}